Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:05.00,ch-note,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs25}我明白你的想法 先請聽我説 \N情況正如你所知 我們應該再一次奮起\N決定由數名志同道合的同志創辦出版社\N希望你能理解為這是新的鬥爭方式\N請一定助我們一臂之力 想跟你當面談談

Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:19.84,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしよう　あなたに出逢うまでの私　忘れちゃったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.99,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,風は頬を撫でる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:26.85,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ララバイ　オブ　バードランド♪　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:31.00,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,坂道蹴りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:34.73,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,頼りない影は伸びる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:39.81,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,終わらない夏休みみたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:45.64,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,プールに忍び込んでる気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:51.24,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　服のまま泳ごうよ   跳ねる　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.38,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,衝撃的誘惑スパイラル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:58.67,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,この胸を突き刺すビートはストレンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:02.55,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,それはパッと燃えて消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.36,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,散々な日々も上等　ドレスアップ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:09.63,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,スウィングしてる　ハイなスピード　サラウンド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:13.23,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,それは何ていうダンス？止まらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:19.84,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,行かないで　耳に絡みついてもう離れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:27.40,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,メロディは　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.94,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,恋みたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:19.84,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}自從和你相遇 我已忘了原來的那個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.99,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}風輕撫著臉頰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:26.85,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}猶如小鳥天堂的安眠曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:31.00,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}踢著坡道走著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:34.73,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}孤單的影子慢慢伸長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:39.81,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仿佛這個暑假永遠無法結束一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:45.64,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有種躲進了游泳池的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:51.24,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呐~ 就這麼穿著衣服游吧 瘋起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.38,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}衝擊性的誘惑螺旋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:58.67,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}撞擊胸膛的節奏是如此奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:02.55,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那是瞬間燃起又消逝的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.36,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}狼狽不堪的日子來得正好 盛裝打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:09.63,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}搖擺起來 用歡快的律動 填滿四周
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:13.23,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這究竟是什麼舞步？ 為何無法停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:19.84,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請不要離去 這縈繞於耳畔的旋律已使我無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:27.40,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.94,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}猶如熱戀般

Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.94,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.19,ch-default,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,誒？　耶誕節派對？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:45.79,ch-default,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個也可以去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.01,ch-default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  下周日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:49.58,ch-default,Girls A-B-C-D,0000,0000,0000,,去的 去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.51,ch-default,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,奧林巴斯樂隊的派對的話 會給我們彈電吉他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:55.76,ch-default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,那個  嘛  如果觀眾要求的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:02:00.00,ch-default,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,呐 律醬也會去吧？ 聖誕派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:03.14,ch-default,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,西見同學也一起  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:07.86,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不了  我是不相關的人 還是免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:13.70,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我下周日要去教會的耶誕節聚會 那邊去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.47,ch-default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說　川渕君也是了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.25,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.56,ch-default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,大意了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:24.45,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,丸尾君　我還是去參加派對吧  可以吧？　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.96,ch-default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.18,ch-default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,熱烈歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:30.96,ch-default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}西見君能答應過來  好開心呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:33.95,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一點點拉開距離就好 一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.01,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.43,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,你晚了哦  公子太郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.93,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.69,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,好咧  接下來是spiders哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.98,ch-default,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,誒！？　披頭四呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.44,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,『bang・bang・bang』  來一發喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.35,ch-default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,西見同學  汽水可以的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.52,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.37,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,「一臉裝傻的表情  bang・bang・bang」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.66,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,「bang・bang  bang・bang・bang・bang  bang・bang・bang・bang」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.85,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,「那傢伙  實在是服了他了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.35,ch-default,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,「bang・bang  bang・bang・bang・bang  bang・bang・bang・bang」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.29,ch-default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,西見同學  來啊 一起來唱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.56,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我對流行的歌不太瞭解…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:39.14,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  現在不知道怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.58,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,在教會和律醬談心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:11.25,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,特意去了派對  卻滿腦子在想那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.53,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我真是傻得可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.11,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,薫同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.40,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,律醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.70,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？  今天不是去教會的麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:25.88,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 教會的聖誕聚會結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.66,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,沒和那傢伙在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.96,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,不在一起就不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.59,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,那個…　他已經回去了  和孩子們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.56,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.59,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,挺冷的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.60,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.31,ch-default,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,you will  hey  come on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.27,ch-default,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,I gotcha you babe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.96,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,話說  馬上要到他生日了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.26,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,能趕上就好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:13.75,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.25,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說這樣的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.59,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:19.53,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.59,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了！　薫同學你這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.93,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,我這又是犯了什麼錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.13,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.44,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,好難懂  女人心真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:42.07,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會發那麼大的火？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:47.41,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,歸根結底  還不是因為我把薫同學甩了  才會這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:53.40,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西就算織了  也不可能送得出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.43,ch-default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,真是鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:30.12,ch-default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,你身體沒有發現異常  但是　百合香 我跟你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.62,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  是讓我不要再見他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.50,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼反復說 也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.41,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,chet！　不行的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.43,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,chet！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.98,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎？  你怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.73,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,什麼為什麼  不是在等你來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.51,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼事　突然一本正經的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.80,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,律子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.35,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:16.86,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,我之前一直沒能察覺到你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:21.87,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,可能說了很多不知輕重的話 傷到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:26.72,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不住了  但是…  那個… 怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.99,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,我  對你的心意  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:42.98,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,千太郎真是的  突然之間一臉反常的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:46.92,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣了  又不是拍黑幫電影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.22,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,是我誤會了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.58,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你誤會了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:08:02.27,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥  原來是誤會了  不好意思  說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:06.93,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  咱們本來就是一家人一樣的麼  真是 討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:11.37,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,這 這樣的話  就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:19.46,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,那個…　如果讓家人一樣的你傷心了 我心裡會不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:28.47,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,幸好聽到剛才那番話的  不是之前的那個我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.11,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,這話咋講
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.71,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,對遲鈍的孩子呀  一輩子也不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.92,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,我有話必須跟你講
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.68,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,我決定這兩天就回東京去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:59.35,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕  和你不會再見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:07.33,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,大學的前輩說要成立出版公司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.32,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,希望我去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.78,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,新年一過 就打算動身過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.28,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,雖然走了很多彎路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.71,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我決心再次上路  都歸功於你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.85,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.73,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 我才不要你說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.84,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,不要從我面前消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.59,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這種話又說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.80,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 好不容易又肯重新振作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.81,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,律子醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.41,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,百合香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.51,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.15,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,在找東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.49,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心把重要的東西扔了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.40,ch-default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個女孩…　是無家可歸麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.69,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,我說　律子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.75,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我了  請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:03.06,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,百合香小姐這麼漂亮乾淨的人  在這種地方可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.13,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,律子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.23,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.31,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,請別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.64,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,不是說是重要的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.34,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,百合香小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:23.80,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你是在找什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:28.69,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.79,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.82,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:35.32,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,不過 得用乾淨的毛線從頭再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.95,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,這是  要送給誰的禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.88,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.50,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會扔掉的呢  這麼重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.75,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我腦子一時錯亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:57.58,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,織這種根本沒法子送出去的東西 一下子覺得自己好傻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.63,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼送不出去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:03.68,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  因為和那人之間的種種糾葛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.61,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,因為曾經狠狠地傷過他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:07.85,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕過他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.77,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 也不好說什麼喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.02,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,就算了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.78,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,可是 又覺得這樣無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:21.65,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有過一次什麼都沒有說出口就放棄的經歷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.50,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,後悔麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:29.18,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是  那件事很久之前就已經放下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:33.19,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,況且我察覺到了 至今為止我情緒低落的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:36.94,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,過來幫我渡過難關的一直都是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:42.68,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,拼命鼓勵沒有自信的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:46.02,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次 我要好好表達出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:51.38,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,我決定不再默默地等待結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.86,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  說了這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.39,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  能聽到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.97,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.39,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.64,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 是誰呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.16,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,律子醬的王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.11,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.31,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來猜猜看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.47,ch-default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀  請不要這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.57,ch-default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.74,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,對  週末打算動身過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.61,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,在東京工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.22,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大學因為諸多事由  退學了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:47.82,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不過  偶爾還是會回來的吧  像以往那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.48,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會再回這個地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.53,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,薫君　之前的合奏很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.86,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不能再見面會很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.19,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,你和千少不要放棄爵士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:05.83,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,淳哥！ 去東京的事已經跟那傢伙說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.60,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,喂　千！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.12,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,咋了 公子哥 臉色都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.38,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 淳哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.31,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是說馬上要去東京的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.82,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,大叔告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.32,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 跟我也沒啥關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.29,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,來！　合奏一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.44,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣不打算再見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.45,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,見了要說啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:41.01,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你從小就一直仰慕著的大哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:45.52,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的人  可能一輩子都見不到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.10,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,就算見了 也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.47,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,等真的分開了就晚了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.16,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止吧 關於淳哥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.73,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,快點開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.71,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,沒心思練習的話  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.74,ch-default,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,這是在鬧什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:20.44,ch-default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,反對原子能航空母艦進駐港口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:24.26,ch-default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,東京啊很多地方的學生都過來示威靜坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.60,ch-default,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.47,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,對他們來講 我是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.48,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,也許一直會被叱責下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.49,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.99,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,往後 我只有用自己的方式來尋求道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.80,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,用與他們不同的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:58.88,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你來了啊 公子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:14:59.97,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,這個吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.94,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,我捏的  可能鹹了點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.35,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃的話  我吃了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.93,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡是吃飯團的時候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.85,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,之前我說的話 都忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.17,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.43,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,少裝蒜了 難道到最後都要意氣用事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:22.68,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,淳哥不是今天就是明天  馬上要離開這個小鎮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.16,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.49,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,是今天的夜行車　薫君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:34.24,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,千少  你送過來的東西還真是老式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:35.00,ch-note,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(736,412)}決\N鬥\N書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.27,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.10,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,可不是什麼開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.91,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,早就想跟淳哥一決勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:47.05,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不會真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.30,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.74,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也加入進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.32,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這已經超越你唱我合的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.07,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,這是兩人之間動真格的打架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:29.30,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  抱歉了  給你添了很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.03,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:35.16,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 一到了東京  先去那個  去理髮店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.54,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.41,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.37,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,淳哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:50.58,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,今天的合奏  我一輩子都不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:57.23,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是 千少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:15.59,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你在這裡？  跟你說了不要來送行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.08,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,想要你回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:21.58,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,如果你回避問題的話  我會坐上這列車的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.33,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你好好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:29.81,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,問題1  為什麼要拒絕我的送行？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:34.43,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡告別這種鬱悶的場合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.23,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,問題2 都沒有想過要帶我一起走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:43.42,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要去做的工作 是一種賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:46.30,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,就算帶你走  生計也無法保證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.42,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,況且 你還只是高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.86,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,問題3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.30,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對我止步於接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:19:00.26,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,不動我一個手指頭 是因為一開始就打算要和我分手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:09.47,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也明白  你這是出於珍惜我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.51,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,問題 這是最後一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.85,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不願帶我走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:24.52,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你珍惜自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:35.80,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.53,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 我也不再糾結猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:43.05,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我會回到我的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.73,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你　淳一先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:48.54,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.67,ch-default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,百合香！  你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.55,ch-default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來　百合香！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.09,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,相親到一半偷偷跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.04,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣讓父母丟臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.55,ch-default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,老公  你小聲點…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.06,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們一起回去  百合香！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:08.06,ch-default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,百合香　在哪裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:18.27,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,我會回到我的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.77,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,把你拖上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.50,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:49.53,ch-default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢？  已經發車了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:50.77,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:55.39,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到了那邊  先去房間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.78,ch-default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,幫我把這頭長髮剪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.61,ch-default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,今天可真是夠冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:11.45,ch-default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,噢  開暖爐吧




Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:27.56,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,あの坂道で君を待っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:35.66,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,放課後の約束に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:40.54,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,遠く滲む「さようなら」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:50.29,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,弱くて歪ですぐに壊れそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.97,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,あの頃の僕にね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:22:02.98,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,小さいな翼を　君がくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:08.40,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,夕闇が傾いだ空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:14.17,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,微かな光 探している
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:22.22,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,君が好きだと　好きだと言えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:34.51,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,教科書の隅に書いた手紙は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:39.82,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:43.08,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,届かずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:48.01,ed-jp,,0000,0000,0000,,あの日のまま
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:27.56,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在那坡道上  等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:35.66,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}隨著放學後的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:40.54,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}而漸聲遠去的道別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:50.29,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}弱小而執拗  脆弱而容易受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.97,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那個時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:22:02.98,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}得到了你給予的小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:08.40,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在暮色漸濃的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:14.17,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}尋找微弱的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:22.22,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}如果那時能夠說出喜歡你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:34.51,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}悄悄在教科書的一角寫下的書信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:39.82,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}卻一如當初
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:43.08,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}無論到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:48.01,ed-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}都無法傳達
